snippet.title: Cold Comfort Pitch
snippet.description:
[INTERNAL USAGE]

Cold Comfort is an asymmetrical zombie co-op/multiplayer tactical FPS currently under development.

Wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/683190/Cold_Comfort/

Check us out on the social media thingies!

►Website: https://www.coldcomfortgame.com
►Discord Community: https://discord.gg/coldcomfort

►IndieDB: https://www.indiedb.com/games/cold-comfort
